## How to run an experiment

```bash
./benchmark.sh > run.log 2>&1
```

The script outputs `METRIC {{metric.name}}=<number>` on success. Extract it:

```bash
grep "^METRIC" run.log
```

If grep returns nothing, the run crashed. Read the last 50 lines of `run.log` for the error.

